						<div class="pdf-file">
				<a href="/fr/content/download/260161/3289028/file/74acfd82052d6197f0089dbd757b72dc.pdf">Télécharger <img src="/extension/agritrade/design/agritrade/images/pdf.gif" alt=""/></a>
